  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates whether offering Tetanus, diphteria and acellular pertussis (Tdap)
      vaccine to caregivers of newborn infants during pediatric well child visits increase the
      caregivers' vaccination rates.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
